#: ../../source/serials.rst:8
msgid "Serials actions can be accessed by going to the 'More' menu at the top of your screen and choosing 'Serials' or by clicking 'Serials' on the main Koha staff interface page. The serials module in Koha is used for keeping track of journals, newspapers and other items that come on a regular schedule."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/serials.rst:13
